<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 06:15:39 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特斯拉进军中国自动驾驶市场面临竞争对手的追赶</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-self-driving-bid-china-faces-rivals-racing-ahead-2024-04-30/</link><description>如果特斯拉成功将其“全自动驾驶”系统引入全球最大的汽车市场中国，这家美国电动汽车先驱将驶入全球自动驾驶汽车竞赛的快车道。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 05:06:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-self-driving-bid-china-faces-rivals-racing-ahead-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>快时尚巨头 Shein 也想销售护肤品、牙膏和玩具</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/fast-fashion-giant-shein-wants-sell-skincare-toothpaste-toys-too-2024-04-30/</link><description>在线快时尚零售商 Shein 正在吸引牙膏集团高露洁棕榄 (Colgate-Palmolive) 和玩具制造商孩之宝 (Hasbro) 等品牌，试图在其平台上销售更多家喻户晓的品牌。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 05:04:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/fast-fashion-giant-shein-wants-sell-skincare-toothpaste-toys-too-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>所罗门群岛投票选出下一任领导人时，亲中国的索加瓦雷退出竞选</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pro-china-sogavare-out-race-solomon-islands-votes-next-leader-2024-04-30/</link><description>所罗门群岛总理马纳西·索加瓦雷(Manasseh Sogavare)拉近了该国与中国的距离，使美国更加关注太平洋岛屿的战略重要性，但在选举结果未果后，他退出了领导人竞选。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 03:25:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pro-china-sogavare-out-race-solomon-islands-votes-next-leader-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国开发商花样年提出新重组条款，股价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-developer-fantasia-proposes-new-restructuring-terms-shares-up-2024-04-30/</link><description>陷入困境的中国房地产开发商花样年周一表示，已与其债券持有人特设小组达成新协议，以新票据和股票重组其 40 亿美元债券。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 03:18:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-developer-fantasia-proposes-new-restructuring-terms-shares-up-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾指责中国在争议激烈的浅滩损坏其船只</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-coast-guard-expels-philippine-vessels-scarborough-shoal-state-media-says-2024-04-30/</link><description>菲律宾周二指责中国海警在南海争议海域骚扰并损坏其一艘船只，并否认北京方面已将两艘船只驱逐出争议激烈的浅滩的立场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 02:35:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-coast-guard-expels-philippine-vessels-scarborough-shoal-state-media-says-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>国际货币基金组织表示，亚洲央行有能力独立于美联储采取行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia-pacific-economies-headed-soft-landing-says-imf-2024-04-30/</link><description>国际货币基金组织周二表示，亚洲相对较低的通胀意味着该地区央行在制定货币政策时可以更多地关注国内状况，而不是美联储可能采取的行动。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 02:23:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia-pacific-economies-headed-soft-landing-says-imf-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>万科首只上市商业REIT上市后早盘下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-vankes-first-public-commercial-reit-falls-early-trade-debut-2024-04-30/</link><description>万科首个公开商业地产投资产品周二上市后早盘下跌高达3%，反映出在房地产市场长期低迷的情况下对中国第二大开发商的谨慎态度。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 02:09:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-vankes-first-public-commercial-reit-falls-early-trade-debut-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市上涨，日元在本周开局波动后波动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-30/</link><description>由于投资者等待一系列经济数据、企业盈利和美联储政策会议，亚洲股市周二小幅走高，而日元在疑似干预措施从 34 年低点提振一天后走软。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 02:04:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>财新PMI显示中国工厂活动创14个月来最快增速</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-factory-activity-expands-fastest-clip-14-months-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-04-30/</link><description>周二的一项私人调查显示，在新出口订单强劲增长的推动下，4月份中国制造业活动以14个月以来最快的速度扩张，这对于仍在努力实现强劲复苏的经济来说是一个令人鼓舞的迹象。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 02:03:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-factory-activity-expands-fastest-clip-14-months-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国四月份工厂和服务业活动放缓削弱了经济势头</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-grows-slower-pace-april-2024-04-30/</link><description>周二的官方调查显示，中国四月份制造业和服务业活动扩张速度均放缓，这表明世界第二大经济体在第二季度初的动力有所减弱。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 01:59:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-grows-slower-pace-april-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>4月份中国非制造业活动扩张放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-non-manufacturing-activity-expands-slower-pace-april-2024-04-30/</link><description>周二的一项官方调查显示，中国四月份非制造业活动扩张速度放缓，可能是由于南方地区恶劣天气对建筑和服务业造成干扰。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 01:41:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-non-manufacturing-activity-expands-slower-pace-april-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国反腐机构对司法部前副部长立案调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-anti-graft-watchdog-probes-former-vice-justice-minister-2024-04-30/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，中国司法部原副部长正接受中央纪委、国家监委纪律审查和监察调查。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 01:19:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-anti-graft-watchdog-probes-former-vice-justice-minister-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>陷入困境的中国城市难以支付购房补贴</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/strained-chinese-cities-struggle-pay-home-buying-subsidies-2024-04-29/</link><description>艾米·王(Amy Wang)指望中国东部城市潍坊当局承诺提供10万元人民币（13,800美元）的补贴来装修她两年前购买的一套公寓。她还在等钱，还没有搬进去。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 23:04:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/strained-chinese-cities-struggle-pay-home-buying-subsidies-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美元兑160日元反弹，特斯拉的中国喜悦</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-04-29/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 21:46:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>秘鲁寻求避免对中国建造的大型港口进行仲裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/peru-seeks-avoid-arbitration-over-chinese-built-mega-port-2024-04-29/</link><description>一位官员周一表示，秘鲁政府正在寻求避免中国港口运营商中远海运可能就该公司正在建造的大型设施的排他权的法律纠纷提起的国际仲裁程序。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 19:51:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/peru-seeks-avoid-arbitration-over-chinese-built-mega-port-2024-04-29/</guid></item></channel></rss>